title: Weds Post Show (04-20-22)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show (04-20-22)
description:
Bobby starts by playing a joke from his Opry set last night about his doctorate. Bobby reveals more details on his comedy shows that he is announcing soon. Bobby talks about a guy going on a sperm donation tour in the US/UK. Eddie spent 2 hours of his day yesterday watching the Johnny Depp trial. Amy has been accused of spoiling TV shows. We talk about the show moving soon. Raymundo also shares that he lost a sponsorship.
